OOC: Excuse me, Jason, but the only way to become a TM3 is with the driver, 
which is currently missing somewhere in the Pred base. You probably dont 
remember, but Vulois, Battera, and Soundwave(deceased) are TM3's. Like i 
always say, im not looking for a fight here. Just think of another way to 
give Cheetor a new body. Oh, and happy birthday Roborick!

:::Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian:::

Starscream: That would be me.  Let me guess- your part of Darkfates team? Is 
the entrance to our new base open yet? Me Bludgeon and Obsidian have been 
waiting awhile.

--part1_95.5afa2f8.2798fcd6_boundary
